summary:
a save about 80 levels breton girl named madona, no quest has been completed yet, even Unbound.

descriptionHtml:
this save is a breton girl, as I said with 81levels,all quest not started exept unbound,and, no perk has been used.She is perfect for those who want to paly as a battlemage because the attributes are add by average.if you dislike the race or how she looks, use the console  command showracemenu, or go to the ragged flagon.
IMPORTANT    patch 1.9 is necessary.
put his file  C:\\Users\\(username)\\Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves
i use a lot of mods, but they are not necessary since its just start the game yet. just load the file. if you have run into any problem,contact me if you want, and your help will be greatly appreciated.
note: i have dawnguard, hearthfire and dragonborn.
         and i will probably update this file.the only mod that affact how she looks should be apachiihair.
